<p>flash插件<br>优点：可以适用大部分的博客，如网易、新浪博客等<br>缺点：无法自己调整插件的高度、宽度<br>auto=1时自动播放,auto=0时否<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;embed src=&quot;//music.163.com/style/swf/widget.swf?sid=152073977&amp;type=0&amp;auto=1&amp;width=310&amp;height=430&quot; width=&quot;330&quot; height=&quot;450&quot;  allowNetworking=&quot;all&quot;&gt;&lt;/embed&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;embed src=&quot;//music.163.com/style/swf/widget.swf?sid=152073977&amp;type=0&amp;auto=1&amp;width=310&amp;height=90&quot; width=&quot;330&quot; height=&quot;110&quot;  allowNetworking=&quot;all&quot;&gt;&lt;/embed&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;embed src=&quot;//music.163.com/style/swf/widget.swf?sid=152073977&amp;type=0&amp;auto=1&amp;width=278&amp;height=32&quot; width=&quot;298&quot; height=&quot;52&quot;  allowNetworking=&quot;all&quot;&gt;&lt;/embed&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
